Package: ahritre
Title: R Bindings for the AHRI TRE Runtime and Protocol
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("AHRI TRE", "Maintainers", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "maintainers@example.invalid")
Description: Provides R bindings over the AHRI TRE stable C ABI and public
    JSON protocol. Includes runtime artifact loading, protocol request
    execution, payload handling, and generated command wrappers for TRE
    interfaces.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/AHRIORG/ahri-tre-r
